{"tid":2211149,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者：非暴力抗爭成功率跌","createTime":"2020-09-21T02:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T11:46:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f82b4342a41ec472bdbb680acf493b9ca35d82bc","tid":2211149,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200921/BKCMYDVX6FGIZIU4Q2YFIUMVNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200921%2FBKCMYDVX6FGIZIU4Q2YFIUMVNM%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZojrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=62e66be9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200921%2FBKCMYDVX6FGIZIU4Q2YFIUMVNM%2F&h=8fb7310e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200921/BKCMYDVX6FGIZIU4Q2YFIUMVNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學者：非暴力抗爭成功率跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hpt-HcDVW-2QhDrYdcsXWg92XMM=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSS3ZFT2N5BINHHM6GFDCTFHBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHpt-HcDVW-2QhDrYdcsXWg92XMM%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSS3ZFT2N5BINHHM6GFDCTFHBY.jpg&h=1d2b973b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nErica Chenoweth<br />\n<br />\n近年示威運動此起彼落，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專制政府滲透社交媒體<br />\n<br />\n切諾韋思與拍檔斯蒂芬（Maria Stephan）14年前分析1900年起各場反獨裁暴政示威運動的結果，指非暴力示威成功機會比暴力抗爭高一倍，主要原因是非暴力示威較易提高參與人數基礎，尤其是不少軍警親友參與示威其中，令軍警不忍血腥驅散，而她計算出這個分水嶺，是當參與示威人數達到人口的3.5%。<br />\n<br />\n切諾韋思的新研究集中近年示威，發現兩個趨勢，其一是非暴力抗爭已成主流，2010年至2019年的非暴力抗爭數目，比有紀錄以來的任何一個十年都要多；其二是抗爭成功率下降，現在暴力抗爭失敗率達九成，但非暴力抗爭的成功率，也由1/2減至1/3。<br />\n<br />\n她認為示威失功率下降有多個因素，其中社交媒體雖為示威者帶來很強的動員武器，但專制政府也學懂如何監控和滲透，並利用社交媒體作宣傳和散播假消息。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"5d07e772cf81d94d07aabda7ed0dc6319ffe90ec","tid":2211149,"uid":155095,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"在中國體制下抗爭成功率係0<br />\n<br />\n因為解放軍係唔理人民生死"},{"pid":"d15a7ea3906e31390dea130c99d29581728cab60","tid":2211149,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"唔好話成功率跌，就連生存率近乎「零」喺中国環境下"},{"pid":"94de620e10b41df7bf8cc13b9b2a3122e1b7edf9","tid":2211149,"uid":232766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"原文係所有抗爭嘅成功率都下降，而並非只係非暴力抗爭。<br />\n<br />\nFrom 原文：現在暴力抗爭失敗率達九成，但非暴力抗爭的成功率，也由1/2減至1/3。"},{"pid":"70a82c946f1aaa4ae25a01505a69d415c711e215","tid":2211149,"uid":105976,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"係咪因為過左1900年<br />\n文化水平高既地方都變左民主體制  少左需要上街抗爭<br />\n<br />\n2010~2019仲要抗爭既地區都係大魔頭執政 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db08266180c1e968618a588d915376a794c6ae8","tid":2211149,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5d07e772cf81d94d07aabda7ed0dc6319ffe90ec","tid":2211149,"uid":155095,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"在中國體制下抗爭成功率係0<br />\n<br />\n因為解放軍係唔理人民生死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n一放實槍就輸"},{"pid":"0319c5aee6b6b3bf48aea25cf48dbdd26d057f94","tid":2211149,"uid":175208,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得暴力抗爭好撚失敗9成<br />\n都唔包法國革命，美國獨立"},{"pid":"ed261192c5810d39eb2752fcc0c41aee5259fbbc","tid":2211149,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫩、加泰、白羅斯、泰國、香港抗爭<br />\n目前黎講都未成功"},{"pid":"7175f98d1e2ec70b56b8225a837840a663d5e20c","tid":2211149,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"中國香港人係亞洲最差劣人種之一，失敗係必然嘅，好扯旗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}